2. 1) Can we rename named instance name in SQL server? 
Answer: - No
        Note that Instance Name rename is unsupported. In named instance the server name is in format of ServerName\InstanceName. So, you can change it to NewName\InstanceName but NOT to ServerName\ NewInstanceName.

3) what factors detemine the UNGRACEFUL behaviour of cluster nodes?
- depends on the parameters set in cluster node's configuration.
- i.e specify the no of times cluster service will attempt to restart or failover clustered role in specific period.
  >> Max failures in specified period
  >> period (hours)

